Sure, here is the code for negative scenarios mentioned below:

1. The Kafka topic 3459-DEV-COLLECTION-JSON-DATA-QUEUE is not present


if (!topicExists("3459-DEV-COLLECTION-JSON-DATA-QUEUE")) {
  throw new RuntimeException("Kafka topic 3459-DEV-COLLECTION-JSON-DATA-QUEUE does not exist!");
}


2. The Kafka topic 3459-DEV-COLLECTION-JSON-DATA-QUEUE is not accessible


try {
  producer.send("3459-DEV-COLLECTION-JSON-DATA-QUEUE", "test");
} catch (KafkaException e) {
  if (e.getCause() instanceof NoBrokersAvailableException) {
    throw new RuntimeException("Kafka topic 3459-DEV-COLLECTION-JSON-DATA-QUEUE is not accessible!");
  }
}


3. The Kafka topic 3459-DEV-COLLECTION-AUDIT-QUEUE is not present


if (!topicExists("3459-DEV-COLLECTION-AUDIT-QUEUE")) {
  throw new RuntimeException("Kafka topic 3459-DEV-COLLECTION-AUDIT-QUEUE does not exist!");
}


4. The Kafka topic 3459-DEV-COLLECTION-AUDIT-QUEUE is not accessible


try {
  producer.send("3459-DEV-COLLECTION-AUDIT-QUEUE", "test");
} catch (KafkaException e) {
  if (e.getCause() instanceof NoBrokersAvailableException) {
    throw new RuntimeException("Kafka topic 3459-DEV-COLLECTION-AUDIT-QUEUE is not accessible!");
  }
}


5. The data read for ProgramArgsList does not contain valid params.


if (!ProgramArgsList.contains("input")) {
  throw new RuntimeException("ProgramArgsList does not contain valid params!");
}


6. The data read for ProgramArgsList contain valid params with invalid values.


if (ProgramArgsList.get("input").isEmpty()) {
  throw new RuntimeException("ProgramArgsList contains valid params with invalid values!");
}


